I will be using the **title.ratings.tsv.gz,** datasets found [here](https://datasets.imdbws.com/). The dictionary can be found [here.](https://datasets.imdbws.com/) This data contains information on different shows/movies, and information on their runtimes, genres.

The question I want to explore is whether there was a difference in average runtime among different genres in 2005 and how different it may have been. This is a fun project that may pique the interest of movie buffs.
